Recommends: fonts-liberation
Description: DYMO Connect web service emulator (Linux)
 Emulates the local HTTP/HTTPS API that DYMO Connect for Desktop exposes
 on Windows/Mac, so browser code using dymo.connect.framework.js (such as
 CellarTracker) can print to a DYMO LabelWriter attached to this machine.
 .
 Ships with TLS statically linked against LibreSSL (no OpenSSL runtime
 dependency) and a userscript that patches the DYMO framework so it
 stops refusing to run on Linux.
